data.description: Welcome to the Farmhouse! "Farmhouse style" has become all the rage, but this one is the REAL deal... From the little red barn, to the wide-plank wood floors, to the shiny red apples in the orchard, this home oozes charm, coziness, and authentic country style (with modern upgrades of course!). Inside, you'll find an inviting and warm country kitchen; a large dining room perfect for entertaining, hosting holidays, complete with a propane fireplace you can run for the ambiance or to keep things nice and toasty throughout the home. A dedicated office on the first floor is perfect for work-from-home, or as a craft or workspace/library. Upstairs you'll find another full bath, an expansive primary bedroom, two mid-size bedrooms, and a fourth/fifth tandem bedroom with its' own separate stairway down to the kitchen. Outside, a large pole barn and a smaller barn offer tons of potential- from storage, to livestock, to workshops, there's plenty of room for hobbies, work, or just to keep all of your toys. Completing the package is an expansive lawn, lush field, 100+ year old oaks and maples, and a "mini" orchard with productive trees. Catch this one at sunset and you'll be sold!
